Readback.Enabled detectors comment: Detector indexing starts at 1; element 0 is not used

LEMOTrigger.\\t\\t\\t\\t\\tLEMO Comment: Each LEMO source allows us to select which detectors to read out for a LEMO trigger of that source. There is no detector 0

PrimitivesTrigger.Pileup comment: Combine primitives from THE SAME detector (within the given time window) into a single pileup event. Readout time will be based on the L1 trigger with max amplitude.
PrimitivesTrigger.HV sides comment: Combine primitives from opposite sides of THE SAME HV detector (within the given time window) into a single event. Readout time will be based on the L1 trigger with max amplitude.
PrimitivesTrigger.Prescale comment: Readout waveforms for 1 in N events (set to 0 to never readout)
PrimitivesTrigger.Coincidence comment: Combine primitives from MULTIPLE detectors (within the given time window) into a single coincident event. Readout time will be based on the L1 trigger with max amplitude.

TestSignalTrigger.Prescale comment: Only read out waveforms for 1 in N events

Script.XML:
<?xml version=_1.0_ encoding=_ISO-8859-1_?>
<RunSequence xmlns:xsi=_http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance_ xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation=__>
<Param l=_1_ name=_type_ comment=_Run type: -1 test, 0 bkg, 9 Ba source, 16 laser, 100 IV_ />
<Param l=_2_ name=_comment1_ comment=_Start comment_ />
<ODBSet l=_3_ path=_/Experiment/Edit on start/Data type_>$type</ODBSet>
<Param l=_5_ name=_t_ comment=_Enter total run time in seconds_ />
<ODBSet l=_8_ path=_/Detectors/Det07/ReadoutControl/Phonon pre-pulse length (ms)_>1000</ODBSet>
<ODBSet l=_9_ path=_/Detectors/Det07/ReadoutControl/Phonon post-pulse length (ms)_>1000</ODBSet>
<ODBSet l=_10_ path=_/Detectors/Det07/ReadoutControl/Phonon on-pulse length (ms)_>0</ODBSet>
<Wait l=_11_ for=_seconds_>3</Wait>
